query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from so_user AS u1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'english',
'gis',
'magento',
'mathoverflow')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('7',
'ag.algebraic-geometry',
'arcgis-10.0',
'at.algebraic-topology',
'database',
'gr.group-theory',
'grammar',
'graph-theory',
'javascript',
'magento-1.9',
'phrase-requests',
'single-word-requests',
'theming')
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Benefactor',
'Good Answer',
'Mortarboard',
'Necromancer',
'Organizer',
'Quorum') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
